# Routing Methods

Express provides methods corresponding to HTTP verbs:
- `app.get()`
- `app.post()`
- `app.put()`
- `app.delete()`
- `app.all()` (handles any method)

Each takes a path and one or more handler functions.

```javascript
app.get('/users', (req, res) => {
  res.send('GET /users');
});

app.post('/users', (req, res) => {
  res.send('POST /users');
});
```

